import React from 'react';
import './Login.css'

export default function Login() {
    return ( <
        form >
        <
        label >
        <
        p > Username < /p> <
        input type = "text" / >
        <
        /label> <
        label >
        <
        p > Password < /p> <
        input type = "password" / >
        <
        /label> <
        div >
        <
        button type = "submit" > Login < /button> < /
        div > <
        /form>
    )
}
